## üîß Advanced Configuration

### Custom Zcash Build Options

```bash
# Build with different options
cd ~/zcash

# Clean build
./zcutil/clean.sh

# Configure with specific options
./zcutil/build.sh \
  --disable-tests \
  --disable-mining \
  --with-gui=no

# Parallel build with all cores
./zcutil/build.sh -j$(nproc)

# Single-threaded (for low RAM)
./zcutil/build.sh -j1
```

### Multiple Node Setup

```bash
# Node 1 (Mainnet)
mkdir -p ~/.zcash_mainnet
~/zcash/src/zcashd -datadir=$HOME/.zcash_mainnet -port=8233 -rpcport=8232

# Node 2 (Testnet)
mkdir -p ~/.zcash_testnet
~/zcash/src/zcashd -datadir=$HOME/.zcash_testnet -testnet -port=18233 -rpcport=18232

# Node 3 (Regtest)
mkdir -p ~/.zcash_regtest
~/zcash/src/zcashd -datadir=$HOME/.zcash_regtest -regtest -port=18444 -rpcport=18232
```

### Tor Configuration

```conf
# zcash.conf - Run over Tor
proxy=127.0.0.1:9050
listen=1
onlynet=onion
addnode=zcashsoil4kygkyz.onion
addnode=zcash.rcp.onion
```

```bash
# Install Tor
sudo apt-get install tor

# Configure Tor
# Add to /etc/tor/torrc:
HiddenServiceDir /var/lib/tor/zcash/
HiddenServicePort 8233 127.0.0.1:8233

# Restart Tor
sudo systemctl restart tor

# Get your onion address
sudo cat /var/lib/tor/zcash/hostname
```

### Pruning (Reduce Disk Usage)

```conf
# zcash.conf - Enable pruning
prune=550  # Keep only 550 MB of block data

# WARNING: Cannot serve full blockchain to other nodes
# Cannot use with txindex=1
```

