## üìù Command Line Usage

### Running Commands Directly

```bash
# Get blockchain info
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli getblockchaininfo

# Get wallet balance
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli z_gettotalbalance

# Generate new address
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli z_getnewaddress

# Send transaction
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli z_sendmany "FROM_ADDR" '[{"address":"TO_ADDR","amount":0.01}]'

# Check transaction
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli gettransaction TXID

# Stop node
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli stop
```

### Useful Scripts

**Monitor Sync Progress:**
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# sync_monitor.sh
while true; do
  PROGRESS=$(~/zcash/src/zcash-cli getblockchaininfo | grep verificationprogress | awk '{print $2}' | tr -d ',')
  BLOCKS=$(~/zcash/src/zcash-cli getblockchaininfo | grep '"blocks"' | awk '{print $2}' | tr -d ',')
  echo "Blocks: $BLOCKS | Progress: $PROGRESS"
  sleep 30
done
```

**Auto-Backup Script:**
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# backup_wallet.sh
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)
~/zcash/src/zcash-cli stop
sleep 10
tar -czf ~/backups/wallet_$DATE.tar.gz ~/.zcash/wallet.dat
gpg -c ~/backups/wallet_$DATE.tar.gz
rm ~/backups/wallet_$DATE.tar.gz
~/zcash/src/zcashd -daemon
echo "Backup created: wallet_$DATE.tar.gz.gpg"
```

